<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为了能将<delay20 />漂亮的烟花<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好好地映入眼中，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我有润一润眼睛哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />烟花升空时<delay8 />那声巨响，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />让人情绪高涨呢～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />接下来<delay8 />还能看到
什么样的烟花呢～？！<delay40 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～<delay20 />让人心潮澎湃～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在最喜欢的<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="33" />上
观看的烟花<delay20 />显得尤其美丽，<delay40 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不这么觉得吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />仿佛夜空中盛放了一轮巨大的花朵般，<delay20 />
超～浪漫的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />“烟花虽美，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但<delay8 />不及<tag a="110" b="10" /><tag a="110" b="0" />”<pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我正在积极征募<delay8 />会对我说<delay20 />
这样的话的人哦～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />刚刚升空的那朵烟花，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想用在未来的<tag a="110" b="10" />演唱会<delay8 />
收尾画面中呢～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />烟花<delay20 />“啪”一下发光，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />火花盛放的瞬间，<delay8 />我最喜欢了～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />烟花<delay20 />马上就要放完了。<delay40 />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虚幻如梦般，注视着烟花余烬的我<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不觉得就像一幅画吗？！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再过一会儿，烟花就要放完了，<delay8 />
时间也过得太快了吧～！<delay40 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我还想再看一会儿呢～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />快看快看，<delay8 />你看见了吗？<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />刚刚那个烟花<delay20 />太～漂亮啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>